sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend (Browser / Ajax)
    participant API as Backend REST API
    participant IS as Inventory Filter Service
    participant DB as Database

    U->>FE: Enable "In Stock" filter

    FE->>API: GET /api/products?inStock=true&page=0&size=12

    API->>IS: filterByStock(inStock,page,size)

    IS->>DB: SELECT * FROM PRODUCTS\nWHERE stock > 0\nLIMIT page,size
    DB-->>IS: available products

    IS->>DB: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM PRODUCTS\nWHERE stock > 0
    DB-->>IS: totalElements

    IS-->>API: ProductPage

    API-->>FE: ApiResponse<ProductPage>

    FE-->>U: Display available products